TC01.Measure: Initial E-RAB Establishment Success Rate for Emergency Calls
TC01.SQL: declare @time varchar(50) =DATETIME_VALUE , @moid varchar(200) = UNIQUE_ID_VALUE, @DCVECTOR_INDEX varchar(100) =NODE_NAME_VALUE select CAST(ROUND(avg(result), 2) AS NUMERIC(36,2)) AS kpiValue from(select sum(Final.Result) as result  from (select 100*(SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABSUCCEM)/(SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABATTEM)-SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABATTREATTEM)))*(SUM(D2.PMS1SIGCONNESTABSUCCEM)/SUM(D2.PMS1SIGCONNESTABATTEM))*(SUM(D1.PMERABESTABSUCCINITARP)/SUM(D1.PMERABESTABATTINITARP)) as Result from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLFDD_V_RAW D1,DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLFDD_RAW D2 where D1.DATETIME_ID = D2.DATETIME_ID and D1.MOID = D2.MOID and D1.DATETIME_ID = @time and D1.MOID = @moid and D1.DCVECTOR_INDEX = @DCVECTOR_INDEX UNION select 100*(SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABSUCCEM)/(SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABATTEM)-SUM(D2.PMRRCCONNESTABATTREATTEM)))*(SUM(D2.PMS1SIGCONNESTABSUCCEM)/SUM(D2.PMS1SIGCONNESTABATTEM))*(SUM(D1.PMERABESTABSUCCINITARP)/SUM(D1.PMERABESTABATTINITARP)) as Result from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLTDD_V_RAW D1,DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLTDD_RAW D2 where D1.DATETIME_ID = D2.DATETIME_ID and D1.MOID = D2.MOID and D1.DATETIME_ID = @time and D1.MOID = @moid and D1.DCVECTOR_INDEX = @DCVECTOR_INDEX)Final)A

TC02.Measure: Uplink Baseband Capacity License Utilization Distribution
TC02.SQL: DECLARE @DATETIME varchar(100)= DATETIME_VALUE , @MOID varchar(200)=UNIQUE_ID_VALUE, @DCVECTOR_INDEX varchar(100)=NODE_NAME_VALUE select  Main.Result as kpiValue from (select PMLICULCAPDISTR AS Result from DC_E_ERBS_BBPROCESSINGRESOURCE_V_RAW where MOID  =@MOID and DATETIME_ID = @DATETIME and DCVECTOR_INDEX = @DCVECTOR_INDEX )Main

TC03.SQL: declare @time varchar(50) = DATETIME_VALUE, @moid varchar(200) = UNIQUE_ID_VALUE, @DCVECTOR_INDEX varchar(100) = NODE_NAME_VALUE select CAST(ROUND(avg(result), 2) AS NUMERIC(36,2)) AS kpiValue from(select sum(Final.Result) as result  from (select 100*(sum(D1.PMPRBUSEDULDTCHQCI)/sum(D2.PMPRBAVAILUL)) as Result from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLFDD_V_RAW D1, DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLFDD_RAW D2 where D1.DATETIME_ID = D2.DATETIME_ID and D1.MOID = D2.MOID and D1.DATETIME_ID = @time and D1.MOID = @moid and D1.DCVECTOR_INDEX = @DCVECTOR_INDEX UNION select 100*(sum(D1.PMPRBUSEDULDTCHQCI)/sum(D2.PMPRBAVAILUL)) as Result from DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLTDD_V_RAW D1, DC_E_ERBS_EUTRANCELLTDD_RAW D2 D1.DATETIME_ID = D2.DATETIME_ID and D1.MOID = D2.MOID and D1.DATETIME_ID = @time and  D1.MOID = @moid and D1.DCVECTOR_INDEX = @DCVECTOR_INDEX)Final)A
